---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Services"
  description="Leadership coaching, personal finance consulting, and speaking engagements with Jason Ehlinger."
>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <span class="section-label">What I Offer</span>
    <h1>Real Frameworks.<br/>Real Results.</h1>
    <p>Everything I teach is something I've lived. No theory. No fluff. Just systems that work.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- LEADERSHIP -->
  <section class="section" id="leadership">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:4rem; align-items:start;">
        <div>
          <span class="section-label">Leadership</span>
          <h2 style="font-size:2rem; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">From Manager to Leader</h2>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); margin-bottom:1.25rem; font-size:1.05rem;">Most managers are stuck in the "Operator's Trap" — spending all their time working <em>in</em> the business instead of <em>on</em> it. I'll give you the exact system I used to build a high-performing team at Taika Translations and scale without burning out.</p>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); margin-bottom:2rem;">This isn't soft leadership advice. It's a complete operating system: accountability structures, decision-making frameworks, communication systems, and a mission-driven culture that runs even when you're not in the room.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-dark">Book a Leadership Session</a>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
            <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.5rem; font-size:1.1rem;">High-Accountability Team Building</h3>
            <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem;">Build a team that takes ownership, hits targets, and doesn't need hand-holding. I'll show you the exact accountability structures that work.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
            <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.5rem; font-size:1.1rem;">Strategic Decision-Making</h3>
            <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem;">Stop second-guessing every call. Learn how to make clear, confident decisions using a framework that factors in mission, values, and data.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
            <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.5rem; font-size:1.1rem;">Meeting Systems That Actually Work</h3>
            <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem;">Meetings should solve problems and drive momentum — not drain your team. I'll show you how to run them right.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.5rem; font-size:1.1rem;">Escape the Operator's Trap</h3>
            <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem;">If your business can't run without you for a week, you don't own a business — you own a job. Let's fix that.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FINANCE -->
  <section class="section section-gray" id="finance">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:4rem; align-items:start;">
        <div>
          <span class="section-label">Personal Finance</span>
          <h2 style="font-size:2rem; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Building Wealth From Zero</h2>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); margin-bottom:1.25rem; font-size:1.05rem;">I saved $100k on a military salary. I built a 7-figure company without investors. My wife and I did it the hard way — methodically, without shortcuts. Now I share everything on the <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@Visiontribemoney" target="_blank" style="color:var(--gold);">Vision Tribe Money</a> channel and in private coaching.</p>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); margin-bottom:2rem;">Finance isn't just about numbers. It's about mindset, communication, discipline, and building a life on your own terms. Whether you're just starting out or trying to break through a ceiling, I have a framework for you.</p>
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@Visiontribemoney" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-gold">Watch Free on YouTube</a>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
            <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.5rem; font-size:1.1rem;">Zero-Based Budgeting</h3>
            <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem;">A budget method that doesn't feel like a budget. Every dollar has a job. You stay in control without feeling restricted.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
            <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.5rem; font-size:1.1rem;">Finances in Marriage</h3>
            <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem;">Money is one of the top causes of marital stress. I'll help you and your partner get on the same page and build toward shared goals.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
            <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.5rem; font-size:1.1rem;">Wealth Building From Nothing</h3>
            <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem;">Starting with $0 isn't a handicap — it's a mindset challenge. Learn the principles and habits that compound into real wealth over time.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.5rem; font-size:1.1rem;">Military & Veteran Finance</h3>
            <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem;">Unique strategies for service members: saving aggressively on base pay, transition planning, and building beyond the BAH mentality.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- COACHING -->
  <section class="section" id="coaching">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:800px; text-align:center;">
      <span class="section-label">1-on-1 Coaching</span>
      <h2 style="font-size:2rem; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Work Directly With Jason</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--gray); margin-bottom:1.25rem; font-size:1.05rem;">Sometimes you need more than content — you need someone who's been where you are, to look at your specific situation and tell you exactly what to do next.</p>
      <p style="color:var(--gray); margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Whether it's a leadership crisis, a financial breakthrough, or you just feel stuck — a 1-on-1 engagement with me will give you clarity, a plan, and accountability to execute.</p>
      <div class="card-grid" style="text-align:left; margin-bottom:2.5rem;">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.5rem; font-size:1.1rem;">Free Assessment Call</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem;">We start by understanding where you are and where you want to go. No pitch. Just an honest assessment and a clear next step.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.5rem; font-size:1.1rem;">Leadership Audit</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem;">A deep dive into your team, systems, and decision-making. You'll walk away with a specific action plan.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.5rem; font-size:1.1rem;">Ongoing Coaching</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem;">Regular sessions for accountability, strategy, and support as you implement your leadership or financial operating system.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-gold" style="font-size:1rem; padding:1rem 2.5rem;">Schedule a Free Assessment</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FREE MASTERCLASSES -->
  <section class="section section-dark text-center">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:600px;">
      <span class="section-label">Free · Every Wednesday</span>
      <h2 style="font-size:2rem; color:var(--white); margin-bottom:1rem;">Weekly Masterclasses</h2>
      <p style="color:#ccc; margin-bottom:2rem;">Join hundreds of leaders and builders every Wednesday for live masterclasses on leadership, money, mindset, and building an unbreakable life.</p>
      <form
        name="masterclass"
        method="POST"
        data-netlify="true"
        style="display:flex; gap:0.75rem; max-width:440px; margin:0 auto; flex-wrap:wrap;"
      >
        <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="masterclass" />
        <input
          type="email"
          name="email"
          placeholder="Your email address"
          required
          style="flex:1; padding:0.85rem 1rem; border:none; border-radius:2px; font-size:1rem; min-width:180px;"
        />
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-gold">Register Free</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    div[style*="grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr"] {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
    }
  }
</style>
